{"tid":567798,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿彭斯見脫北者公布新制裁　朝方突取消冬奧會面","createTime":"2018-02-21T07:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T10:12:27.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a5cb8cd8d5ea8360adb814b76b4dcc46de3d2a04","tid":567798,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T07:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180221/s00005/276fc827ae93651f50da503f87cf2131.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180221%2Fs00005%2F276fc827ae93651f50da503f87cf2131.jpg&h=7bd0e88f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾經多方斡旋，朝鮮終於參加韓國平昌冬奧。國際關注美朝關係會否因此緩解。有美國官員透露，副總統彭斯原定於2月10日在冬奧開幕翌日時，與朝鮮最高領導人金正恩的妹妹金與正，及最高人民會議常任委員會委員長金永南會面，但在會面前兩小時，朝鮮單方面決定取消會議。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯辦公室指，朝鮮突然取消預定安排時，有朝方官員稱不滿彭斯會見在韓的脫北者，及公布將對朝實施更多制裁。彭斯的幕僚長亞耶斯（Nick Ayers）表示，在彭斯譴責朝鮮踐踏人權，並公布計劃實施新一輪制裁後，朝鮮代表「拒絕會面，又或者他們根本無誠意會談」。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人諾爾特（Heather Nauert）指，彭斯已準備好利用今次機會與朝鮮官員見面，藉此表達美方對朝鮮發展核武的關注，對於朝鮮「未能把握這次機會」，美方表示遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180221/s00005/1519196167941\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180221%2Fs00005%2F1519196167941&d=K1AVKCpQm38pRxEEHM3wukjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=09bd0d9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180221%2Fs00005%2F1519196167941&h=0f72921a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180221/s00005/1519196167941</a>"},{"pid":"122693e1602ebf0108f66f1109b005fe72468581","tid":567798,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:48:37.000Z","msg":"完撚左一切照舊"},{"pid":"93851a8808acc793c3a0cfb403887cdf3514be6d","tid":567798,"uid":53705,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"122693e1602ebf0108f66f1109b005fe72468581","tid":567798,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislik